Skills.Name: Normal Attack
Skills.Description: Inflicts 2-hit DMG ({0}% + {1}%) on single enemy. Further cancels 1x Buff effect.
Skills.ShortDescription: Inflicts 2-hit DMG, cancels Buff effect(s) on single enemy

Skills.Name: Their Punishment
Skills.Description:
[If partied with Cid/Shadow]
Raises DMG Received for all enemies by {0}% for 10s. Further increases DMG Received by {1}% for 10s if Yellow Elemental. Inflicts 3-hit DMG (<color=red>{2}%</color> + <color=red>{3}%</color> + <color=red>{4}%</color>) on single enemy. Also inflicts <code=400,param=209><color=#3398f1>Knockback</color> by {5} cm. Further inflicts <code=400,param=202><color=#3398f1>Stun</color> for 3s. Raises DMG Inflicted for Cid/Shadow (ally) by <color=red>{7}%</color> for 10s.
Skills.ShortDescription:
[If partied with Cid/Shadow]
Raises DMG Received for all enemies. Further increases DMG Received if Yellow Elemental. Inflicts 3-hit DMG, Knockback and Stun on single enemy. Raises DMG Inflicted for Cid/Shadow (ally)
Skills.ConditionalSkillDescription:
[If not partied with Cid/Shadow]
Raises DMG Received for all enemies by {0}% for 10s. Further increases DMG Received by {1}% for 10s if Yellow Elemental. Inflicts 3-hit DMG (<color=red>{2}%</color> + <color=red>{3}%</color> + <color=red>{4}%</color>) on single enemy. Also inflicts <code=400,param=209><color=#3398f1>Knockback</color> by {5} cm. Further inflicts <code=400,param=202><color=#3398f1>Stun</color> for 3s. Consumes {8}% HP (Current) of self.
Skills.ConditionalSkillShortDescription:
[If not partied with Cid/Shadow]
Raises DMG Received for all enemies. Further increases DMG Received if Yellow Elemental. Inflicts 3-hit DMG, Knockback and Stun on single enemy. Consumes HP (Current) of self

Skills.Name: Always by Your Side
Skills.Description:
[If partied with Cid/Shadow]
Raises DMG Inflicted for all allies by <color=red>{0}%</color> for 10s. Further increases DMG Inflicted by <color=red>{1}%</color> for 10s if Green Elemental. <code=200,param=115><color=#3398f1>Shields</color> DMG (<color=red>{2}%</color> of skill user's ATK) of Cid/Shadow (ally) for 10s. Further recovers SP by {3}.
Skills.ShortDescription:
[If partied with Cid/Shadow]
Raises DMG Inflicted for all allies. Further increases DMG Inflicted if Green Elemental. Shields DMG, recovers SP of Cid/Shadow (ally)
Skills.ConditionalSkillDescription:
[If not partied with Cid/Shadow]
Raises DMG Inflicted for all allies by <color=red>{0}%</color> for 10s. Further increases DMG Inflicted by <color=red>{1}%</color> for 10s if Green Elemental. Consumes {4}% HP (Current) of self.
Skills.ConditionalSkillShortDescription:
[If not partied with Cid/Shadow]
Raises DMG Inflicted for all allies. Further increases DMG Inflicted if Green Elemental. Consumes HP (Current) of self

Skills.Name: Blind Faith
Skills.Description:
[If partied with Cid/Shadow]
Inflicts 2-hit DMG (<color=red>{0}%</color> + <color=red>{1}%</color>) on all enemies. Further inflicts <code=400,param=256><color=#3398f1>Weakness</color> ({2}% of skill user's ATK) for 8s. Raises DMG Inflicted of self and Cid/Shadow (ally) by <color=red>{3}%</color> for 30s. Also raises Speed by {4}% for 30s. Further raises ATK by <color=red>{5}%</color> for 30s.
Skills.ShortDescription:
[If partied with Cid/Shadow]
Inflicts 2-hit DMG and Weakness on all enemies. Raises DMG Inflicted, Speed and ATK of self and Cid/Shadow (ally)
Skills.ConditionalSkillDescription:
[If not partied with Cid/Shadow]
Inflicts 2-hit DMG (<color=red>{0}%</color> + <color=red>{1}%</color>) on all enemies. Consumes {9}% HP (Current) of self.
Skills.ConditionalSkillShortDescription:
[If not partied with Cid/Shadow]
Inflicts 2-hit DMG on all enemies. Consumes HP (Current) of self

Skills.Name: Strike Combo
Skills.Description: Inflicts <color=red>75.00%-1500.00%</color> DMG according to Combo Bonus. Further inflicts <code=400,param=256><color=#3398f1>Weakness</color> ({1}% of skill user's ATK) for 3s.
Skills.ShortDescription: Inflicts DMG and Weakness on single enemy
